For a number of references, see J. G. McManaway's footnote in Standards of Bibliographical Description (1949), pp. 88-89. See also The Library, 4th ser., XIX (1938), 315-38; 5th ser., II (1947), 20-44;
       5th ser., III (1948), 124-137; Papers Bibl. Soc. America, XLII (1948),
